### Phase 1 — No Authentication
### All requests must return 401 Unauthorized.
### Run WITHOUT any Authorization header.

### Patient resources — no auth
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Content-Type: application/json

###

GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/encounters
Content-Type: application/json

###

GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Admin endpoints — no auth
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/admin/roles
Content-Type: application/json

###

GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Write operations — no auth
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Patient","name":[{"family":"Test"}]}

###

DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients/patient/1/fake-id
Content-Type: application/json

###
